Package: summstats
Title: Statistical Summary Functions for Data Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Zahra", "Alipour", email = "zaralipour@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A collection of functions for calculating summary statistics and
    performing data analysis tasks. This package provides utilities for
    summarizing numeric variables in data frames, with optional grouping
    capabilities.
